- Components: every subfolder has index.ts; widgets use PascalCase and re-export via index.ts; UI components must be reusable.
- Utilities: generic under src/utils, domain-specific under src/helpers; filenames kebab-case.
- Styling: Tailwind CSS only; prefer soft/pastel tones.
- Error handling: wrap API calls with try/catch and user feedback (e.g., toast).
- a11y: use proper aria; wrap images in figure where appropriate.

